---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About — Oli's Blog" description="About Olivia, an NTU CSIE student who writes as Olí.">
  <header class="page-header page-shell"><h1 class="display-title">ABOUT</h1></header>

  <section class="section page-shell about-grid">
    <aside class="profile-card">
      <img src="/images/site/avatar.png" alt="Olí's cloud-and-sky avatar" />
      <div><strong>Olivia</strong><span>Olí</span></div>
      <dl><div><dt>school</dt><dd>NTU</dd></div><div><dt>major</dt><dd>CSIE</dd></div><div><dt>timezone</dt><dd>Asia/Taipei</dd></div></dl>
    </aside>

    <article class="about-copy">
      <section><span class="eyebrow">About this blog</span><h2>想放什麼，就放什麼。</h2><p>不只會有 CS 有關的東西，什麼想放的都放。有些在建立這個部落格之前打過的文章——包括在網路上分享過的東西跟一些後記——也會照以前打的日期放上來。</p></section>

      <section><span class="eyebrow">About me</span><h2>從「寫程式很帥」開始。</h2><p>我是 Olivia，在網路上通常叫 oliiiiiiiiii，學了西班牙文後更喜歡用 Olí。我目前大二，就讀台大資工系。</p><blockquote>國三的時候一直覺得寫程式很帥，所以立定志向要考台大資工。升高一的暑假開始接觸 C++，寫得越多就發現自己越喜歡。</blockquote><p>高中參加過資訊之芽語法班，也曾經在數學競賽裡隨緣探索；現在繼續把寫程式、學習和分享這些事情放在一起。</p></section>

      <section><span class="eyebrow">Other learnings</span><h2>不只 Computer Science。</h2><p>大一的時候不想修大一英文，所以選了西班牙文，學了一陣子之後發現自己還蠻喜歡的，因此決定持續好好學。從小也很喜歡教學，對教育一直很有興趣。</p></section>

      <section class="contacts"><span class="eyebrow">Contacts</span><h2>Find me online.</h2><div><a href="https://www.instagram.com/_y.chen_0108/" rel="noreferrer"><small>instagram</small><strong>@_y.chen_0108 ↗</strong></a><a href="https://github.com/oliiiiiiiiii" rel="noreferrer"><small>github</small><strong>@oliiiiiiiiii ↗</strong></a><a href="https://discord.com/users/801441766330859570" rel="noreferrer"><small>discord</small><strong>Olí. ↗</strong></a><a href="mailto:olivia950108@gmail.com"><small>email</small><strong>olivia950108@gmail.com ↗</strong></a></div></section>
    </article>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: minmax(250px, .55fr) minmax(0, 1.45fr); align-items: start; gap: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 8rem); }
  .profile-card { position: sticky; top: 2rem; overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: var(--radius-sm); background: var(--surface); box-shadow: var(--shadow-md); }
  .profile-card > img { width: 100%; aspect-ratio: 1; display: block; object-fit: cover; }
  .profile-card > div { padding: 1rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); }.profile-card strong,.profile-card span { display: block; }.profile-card strong { font-size: 1rem; }.profile-card span { margin-top: .2rem; color: var(--muted); font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: .65rem; }
  dl { padding: .7rem 1rem 1rem; margin: 0; font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: .64rem; }dl div { padding-block: .3rem; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; gap: 1rem; }dt { color: var(--teal); }dd { margin: 0; color: var(--muted); }
  .about-copy { display: grid; gap: 4rem; }.about-copy h2 { margin: .55rem 0 1rem; font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 3rem); letter-spacing: -.035em; line-height: 1.1; }.about-copy p { color: var(--ink-soft); line-height: 1.9; }.about-copy blockquote { margin: 1.5rem 0; padding: .3rem 0 .3rem 1.25rem; color: var(--ink); border-left: 3px solid var(--teal); font-family: var(--font-serif); font-size: 1.08rem; line-height: 1.8; }
  .contacts > div { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr)); gap: .7rem; }.contacts a { padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: var(--radius-sm); background: var(--surface); text-decoration: none; }.contacts a:hover { border-color: var(--teal); }.contacts small,.contacts strong { display: block; }.contacts small { color: var(--teal); font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: .6rem; }.contacts strong { margin-top: .25rem; font-size: .83rem; overflow-wrap: anywhere; }
  @media (max-width: 850px) { .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }.profile-card { position: static; max-width: 360px; } }
  @media (max-width: 560px) { .contacts > div { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
</style>
